modifications_json.description:
JSON array of modification entries. Each entry has a `type` and type-specific fields:
  SetCurve    { type, componentType, propertyName, relativePath?, keyframes: [{time, value, inTangent?, outTangent?}] }
  RemoveCurve { type, componentType, propertyName, relativePath? }
  ClearCurves { type }
  SetFrameRate { type, frameRate }
  SetWrapMode  { type, wrapMode (Default/Once/Loop/PingPong/ClampForever) }
  SetLegacy    { type, legacy (bool) }
  AddEvent     { type, time, functionName, floatParameter?, intParameter?, stringParameter? }
  ClearEvents  { type }

JSON array of modification entries. Each entry has a `type` and type-specific fields:
  AddParameter          { type, parameterName, parameterType (Float/Int/Bool/Trigger), defaultFloat?, defaultInt?, defaultBool? }
  RemoveParameter       { type, parameterName }
  AddLayer              { type, layerName }
  RemoveLayer           { type, layerName }
  AddState              { type, layerName, stateName, motionAssetPath? }
  RemoveState           { type, layerName, stateName }
  SetDefaultState       { type, layerName, stateName }
  AddTransition         { type, layerName, sourceStateName, destinationStateName, hasExitTime?, exitTime?, duration?, hasFixedDuration?, conditions?: [{parameter, mode (If/IfNot/Greater/Less/Equals/NotEqual), threshold?}] }
  RemoveTransition      { type, layerName, sourceStateName, destinationStateName }
  AddAnyStateTransition { type, layerName, destinationStateName, hasExitTime?, duration?, conditions?: [...] }
  SetStateMotion        { type, layerName, stateName, motionAssetPath }
  SetStateSpeed         { type, layerName, stateName, speed }
